import * as React from 'react' import './pageSeven.css' import Title from './components/title_bar' import Navbar from './components/nav_bar' import Font from './components/fnt_sze' export default function Imprint(){ const [Lang,SetLang]=React.useState('EN') let LangEN,LangDE; if(Lang === 'EN'){ LangEN = 'block' LangDE = 'none' } else if (Lang === 'DE'){ LangDE='block' LangEN='none' } const [Fntsze,SetFntsze]=React.useState(20) return(
<Navbar onUpdate = {(value:string)=>SetLang(value)}/> <div className = "txt_box"> <h1 style={{display:LangEN}}>Imprint</h1> <h1 style={{display:LangDE}}>Impressum</h1> <Font fntSlct={(sze:number)=>SetFntsze(sze)}/> <hr></hr> <p style={{display:LangEN, fontSize:Fntsze}}> <b>Declarations according to § 5 TMG</b> <br></br> <br></br> Registered in the register of associations, city of Jülich, VR 227 <br></br> <br></br> Postal address: <br></br> <br></br> Münchenerstraße - 4, <br></br> <br></br> 52428, Jülich <br></br> <br></br> Contact: E-Mail: info@int-club-juelich.de </p> </div> </div> ) }
